<h3 id="imageshape">图片形状</h3>
<p>通过为<code>img</code>元素添加以下相应的类，可以让图片呈现不同的形状。</p>
    <blockquote class="blockquote-danger">
        <p class="blockquote_img">跨浏览器兼容性</p>
        <small>请时刻牢记：<code>Internet Explorer 8</code> 不支持 CSS3 中的圆角属性。</small>
    </blockquote>
<div class="well">
    <div class="highlight">
         <div class="bs-example bs-example-images" data-example-id="image-shapes">
            <img data-holder-rendered="true" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," style="width: 140px; height: 140px;" data-src="holder.js/140x140" class="img-rounded" alt="140x140">
            <img data-holder-rendered="true" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," style="width: 140px; height: 140px;" data-src="holder.js/140x140" class="img-circle" alt="140x140">
            <img data-holder-rendered="true" src="data:image/svg+xml;base64," style="width: 140px; height: 140px;" data-src="holder.js/140x140" class="img-thumbnail" alt="140x140">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight">
        <h4>示例代码：</h4>
        <div class="well mbn">
    <pre class="brush:xml">
        <img src="..." alt="..." class="img-rounded">
        <img src="..." alt="..." class="img-circle">
        <img src="..." alt="..." class="img-thumbnail">
    </pre>
